# Title: Nslookup PowerShell Download Cradle - ProcessCreation
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-09-05
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects suspicious powershell download cradle using nslookup. This cradle uses nslookup to extract payloads from DNS records
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_nslookup_poweshell_download.yml

CommandLine IN ("* -q=txt *", "* -querytype=txt *") ParentImage IN ("*\\powershell.exe", "*\\pwsh.exe") Image="*\\nslookup.exe*" OR OriginalFileName="\\nslookup.exe"